{
  "texts": [
    "Ethics approval by the institutional committee (Ethics Committee of University of Pannonia) is not required specifically for this research.",
    "Personal data is adequately protected, making it impossible to infer personal consequences.",
    "Trends and patterns were the focus of the research, which only make it possible to characterize a certain population.",
    "For this type of research, the Code of Ethics states that the Ethics Committee does not require prior approval of the research.",
    "The authors declare that there are no ethical issues with the results presented."
  ]
}